"2 pounds purple potatoes (about 1 /2 in. thick)","2  yellow crookneck squash (about 1/4 lb. each)","1/4 pound tomatillos","1  red bell pepper (1/2 lb.)","1  poblano chili (about 3 oz.)","1 cup orange juice","1/2 cup lime juice","  Sugar (optional)","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro","  Salt"